### customers-redact 正常
POST {{API_BASE}}/api/webhook/customers-redact
X-Shopify-Hmac-SHA256: {{HMAC}}
X-Shopify-Webhook-Id: {{WEBHOOK_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shop_domain": "{{SHOP_DOMAIN}}",
  "customer": { "id": 1234567890, "email": "user@example.com" },
  "orders_to_redact": [111,222]
}

### customers-redact 重複（IdempotencyKeyで抑止）
POST {{API_BASE}}/api/webhook/customers-redact
X-Shopify-Hmac-SHA256: {{HMAC}}
X-Shopify-Webhook-Id: {{WEBHOOK_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shop_domain": "{{SHOP_DOMAIN}}",
  "customer": { "id": 1234567890, "email": "user@example.com" },
  "orders_to_redact": [111,222]
}

### app/uninstalled 正常
POST {{API_BASE}}/api/webhook/uninstalled
X-Shopify-Hmac-SHA256: {{HMAC}}
X-Shopify-Webhook-Id: {{WEBHOOK_ID2}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "domain": "{{SHOP_DOMAIN}}",
  "id": 987654321
}

### HMAC不正（403想定）
POST {{API_BASE}}/api/webhook/customers-data-request
X-Shopify-Hmac-SHA256: invalid-hmac
X-Shopify-Webhook-Id: {{WEBHOOK_ID3}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shop_domain": "{{SHOP_DOMAIN}}",
  "customer": { "id": 555, "email": "bad@example.com" },
  "data_request": { "id": 333 }
}


